                  </persName>
            . I am an apprentice to Mr. Guest, pawnbroker, Fleet Market. On the 21st of August I took in two table-spoons of the prisoner, I advanced half a guinea on them; the tea-spoon was taken in by a young man in the shop, he is not here.</p>
